  "title": "Three people saw a cigar-shaped UFO in Curitiba [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/17/three-people-saw-a-cigar-shaped-ufo-in-curitiba-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uk",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 10th, 1999</strong>. Time: 00h30. Duration: 4 seconds. Three people in the Batel neighborhood in Curitiba, State of Paraná, spotted an unidentified flying object shaped like a cigar with 4 meters in size. According to witnesses, the UFO flew at a low altitude, 50m, and its color oscillated between gray and fluorescent green. The object was approximately 1km away from the observers, but close enough for them to perceive a vibration from the UFO. Soon after being noticed at low speed, the object proceeded very fast towards the South.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.560. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Avistamento de ovni no bairro de Batel, Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
